gantt
    title CCRB Year 1 Phased Timeline
    dateFormat YYYY-MM
    axisFormat %b

    section Startup
    Execute subrecipient MOAs; hire/onboard 4.0 FTE; establish data systems  :a1, 2025-10, 1M

    section Infrastructure
    HCJPD referral protocols; staff training; JI-RPS orientation              :a2, 2025-10, 2M

    section Launch
    Launch SCBF at CUPS; deploy literacy screening; procure naloxone           :a3, 2025-11, 1M

    section Enrollment
    Begin court intake; Cohort 1 (12-15 youth); MOUD assessments              :a4, 2025-11, 2M

    section Family Services
    Certified Family Partner services launch (education, home visits, resource linkage) :a5, 2025-12, 1M

    section Full Operations
    Full 90-day cycles; YRC established; baseline evaluation; community linkages :a6, 2025-12, 4M

    section Mid-Year
    Mid-year assessment + OAFC report; validate 14-day assessment and initiation targets :a7, 2026-03, 1M

    section Continuous
    Continuous enrollment; YRC continuing care; RSPS apprenticeships (18+)     :a8, 2026-04, 6M

    section Year-End
    Year 1 comprehensive report; sustainability + Medicaid exploration          :a9, 2026-09, 1M
